## WithAccessControlMetadata interface

With FGAC, the backend will return additional access control metadata to objects. These metadata will contain user permissions associated to a given resource.

For example: { accessControl: { "datasources:read": true, "datasources:write": true } }

<b>Signature</b>

```typescript
export interface WithAccessControlMetadata 
```
<b>Import</b>

```typescript
import { WithAccessControlMetadata } from '@grafana/data';
```
